ustainability and Safety:<\/strong><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">In order to ensure the long term sustainability of these these wells, a\u00a0water user committee will be formed at each location. Each committee shall be comprised of 10 to 20 community notables who will represent local communities. The water wells will be handed over to the water user committees through an agreement. Moreover, the water committees shall be responsible for the regular maintenance of the water well through contributions from the water users.<\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<h2>Donate Online<\/h2>\n<figure id=\"attachment_1081\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-1081\" style=\"width: 170px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><a title=\"Water-wells &amp;  Hand-pumps\" href=\"https:\/\/uk.virginmoneygiving.com\/fundraiser-web\/donate\/makeDonationForFundraiserDisplay.action?fundraiserActivityId=443251\" target=\"_blank\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-1081\" src=\"https:\/\/qidwaiwelfare.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2014\/04\/165040045c.jpg\" alt=\"Water-wells &amp; Hand-pumps\" width=\"170\" height=\"125\" \/><\/a><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-1081\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Tharparkar Water-wells<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Online donations will be made in British Pounds, and \u00a31.00 = $1.67, and \u00a31.00 = KD 0.475.<\/p>\n<h2>Donate via bank wire transfer<\/h2>\n<h3><strong>Pakistan<\/strong><\/h3>\n<p><strong>Account Name &#8211;<\/strong>\u00a0Qidwai Welfare Trust<\/p>\n<p><strong>Account Number &#8211;<\/strong>\u00a00055001586000087<\/p>\n<p><strong>IBAN Number &#8211;<\/strong>\u00a0PK93BURJ0055001586000087<\/p>\n<p><strong>Bank Name &#8211;<\/strong>\u00a0Burj Bank Ltd.<\/p>\n<p><strong>Address &#8211;<\/strong>\u00a0F8 Markaz Branch, Islamabad, Pakistan<\/p>\n<p><strong>Swift Code &#8211;\u00a0<\/strong>BURJPKKAXXX<\/p>\n<p><strong>Currency &#8211;\u00a0<\/strong>Pakistani Rupee<\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<h3><strong>United Kingdom\u0